%C A220084 Other sequences of numbers of the form m*P(k,m)-(m-1)*P(k,m-1), where P(k,m) is the m-th k-gonal pyramidal number:
%C A220084 k=3, A002412(m) = m*A000292(m)-(m-1)*A000292(m-1);
